Crystal shards in soil near the trial sites are not inert residue but active components of still-operating resonance matrices; removing them disrupts local circuit continuity and can trigger unpredictable energy redistribution in the surrounding network.
Rivennid assessment: the Withered Depths cannot be healed without addressing the trial site matrices, and the trial site matrices cannot be addressed without understanding the full extent of the Verdant Depths' counter-response.

